{
  "page": "Council of magisters (Lorath)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>council of magisters</b> is the governing body of the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free City</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Lorath\" title=\"Lorath\">Lorath</a>. It is composed of nobles, priests and merchants.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Even though the city is nominally ruled by a council of three princes formed by the <a href=\"/index.php/Harvest_Prince\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Harvest Prince\">Harvest Prince</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Fisher_Prince\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fisher Prince\">Fisher Prince</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_the_Streets\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prince of the Streets\">Prince of the Streets</a>, true power lies in the council of magisters.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Council_of_magisters_(Lorath)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The true authority resides with a council of <a href=\"/index.php/Magister\" title=\"Magister\">magisters</a> made up of nobles, priests, and merchants.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Council_of_magisters_(Lorath)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: Lorath.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404215303\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.015 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.016 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 264/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8682/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1341/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 575/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1297/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclu